defaultNorthumberland County Council is 
defaultusing the informa
defaulttion collected in these parish surveys to help in its financial review of the bus services which it supports. If the key issues 
defaultof information, routes and regularity 
defaultcan be addressed bus usage will increase. In fact operators have already noticed an increa
defaultse in passenger numbers since the surveys were conducted. 
defaultP
defaultlans for supported services from 2014 onwards currently being finalised by 
defaultNorthumberland
default County Council and should result in a more regular timetable
defaults
